Meaning if you are planning on keeping it on for a longer duration at stretch, then it becomes more expensive because you will have to use 3 AA cells every other day.Better to go for usb led lights or direct electric light.I do not recommend this product.
Loved them.... Lights up the ambience!

It's exactly as described and works perfectly. Very useful for decoration ideas. It was wrapped properly and every LED works perfectly.Very happy with the product. It's a must buy.
